Source: grml-debugtools
Section: grml
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Michael Gebetsroither <gebi@grml.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 4.0.0), libglib2.0-dev, libboost-dev, libstdc++-dev, xsltproc, docbook-xsl, asciidoc, libgebi-dev (>= 0.08)
Standards-Version: 3.6.2

Package: grml-debugtools
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Various debug related tools
 This tools help in tracking down complicated problems:
 sh-wrapper - wrapper for /bin/sh which logs information about caller to syslog
 event-viewer - program to see all fork/exec/exit/uid/gid events
 bench - simple benchmarking utility
